Package xmlElements

The package xmlElements contains all the classes that can be marshalled by JaxB in our project, ie : The different response from the APIs (Nominatim, Overpass) The request and the query format for the services of our server (smallestCommonPath, geoScalePathsInArea) the class GeoScalePath that can also be marshalled.

The package xmlElements contains all the classes that can be marshalled by JaxB in our project, ie : The different response from the APIs (Nominatim, Overpass) The request and the query format for the services of our server (smallestCommonPath, geoScalePathsInArea) the class GeoScalePath that can also be marshalled.
